Package: HealthCAAnalysis
Title: Health Behavior Correspondence Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-01-01
Description: Correspondence analysis and hierarchical clustering applied to CDC
    health survey data. Explores associations between self-rated health status
    and behavioral variables including exercise participation, smoking history,
    health plan coverage, and gender.
Imports:
    FactoMineR (>= 2.8),
    factoextra (>= 1.0.7),
    dplyr (>= 1.1.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.0),
    scales (>= 1.2.0)
Suggests:
    ggrepel (>= 0.9.3),
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
